      <title>CentOS下Django部属</title>
      <link href="/2019/03/04/centos-install-python/"/>
      <url>/2019/03/04/centos-install-python/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Django 2.1 开发与部属记录</p><h2 id="1-安装MySQl"><a href="#1-安装MySQl" class="headerlink" title="1. 安装MySQl"></a>1. 安装MySQl</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum localinstall https://dev.mysql.com/get/mysql57-community-release-el7-9.noarch.rpm</span><br><span class="line">yum -y install mysql-community-server</span><br><span class="line">systemctl start mysqld</span><br><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> mysqld</span><br><span class="line">netstat -plntu</span><br><span class="line">systemctl is-enabled mysqld</span><br><span class="line">grep <span class="string">'temporary'</span> /var/<span class="built_in">log</span>/mysqld.log</span><br><span class="line">mysql -u root -p</span><br><span class="line">TYPE DEFAULT PASSWORD</span><br><span class="line">ALTER USER <span class="string">'root'</span>@<span class="string">'localhost'</span> IDENTIFIED BY <span class="string">'Newhakase-labs123@'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">flush privileges;</span><br><span class="line">-- upgrade from old version, please backup data at first</span><br><span class="line">mysql_upgrade -u root -p</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-1配置-MySQL-编码"><a href="#1-1配置-MySQL-编码" class="headerlink" title="1.1配置 MySQL 编码"></a>1.1配置 MySQL 编码</h3><p>[mysqld]<br>character-set-server=utf8<br>collation-server=utf8_general_ci</p><h2 id="2-安装Python2-Python3"><a href="#2-安装Python2-Python3" class="headerlink" title="2. 安装Python2 / Python3"></a>2. 安装Python2 / Python3</h2><h3 id="2-1-安装python-27"><a href="#2-1-安装python-27" class="headerlink" title="2.1 安装python 27"></a>2.1 安装python 27</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo yum install epel-release</span><br><span class="line">yum -y install python-pip</span><br><span class="line">yum -y install python-virtualenv</span><br><span class="line">yum -y install python-virtualenvwrapper</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-2-安装python-35"><a href="#2-2-安装python-35" class="headerlink" title="2.2 安装python 35"></a>2.2 安装python 35</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo yum install centos-release-scl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可选择安装如下版本中的一个:<br>   Python 3.3<br>   Python 3.4<br>   Python 3.5<br>   Python 3.6<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo yum install rh-python35</span><br><span class="line">scl <span class="built_in">enable</span> rh-python35 bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="3-CentOS的防火墙配置"><a href="#3-CentOS的防火墙配置" class="headerlink" title="3. CentOS的防火墙配置"></a>3. CentOS的防火墙配置</h2><p>这里开启了8000端口<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">firewall-cmd --get-active-zones  </span><br><span class="line">firewall-cmd --zone=public --list-ports</span><br><span class="line">firewall-cmd --zone=public --permanent --add-port=8000/tcp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="4-Django配合gunicorn的启动脚本"><a href="#4-Django配合gunicorn的启动脚本" class="headerlink" title="4. Django配合gunicorn的启动脚本"></a>4. Django配合gunicorn的启动脚本</h2><p>start.sh<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scl <span class="built_in">enable</span> rh-python35  <span class="string">"source /root/task_management/venv/bin/activate &amp;&amp; gunicorn -w 8  --bind 0.0.0.0:8000 api.wsgi"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
